OL,4,G0900FAbandoned Engineering
OL,5,     GLearn more about an American
OL,6,     Ginstallation that waged the Cold
OL,7,     GWar, a derelict ruin on a sand
OL,8,     Gdune, an industrial site lost in
OL,9,     Ga forest and an abandoned tower.
OL,10,G1000FAbandoned Engineering
OL,11,     GStrange structures rusting away
OL,12,     Gat sea. Once cutting-edge in
OL,13,     Gdesign and construction, they now
OL,14,     Glie disused, contaminated and
OL,15,     Gdangerous. But who built them?
OL,16,     GAnd why were they abandoned?
